Value: Locksley Resources Limited, a minerals exploration company, engages in identifying, exploring, and developing copper and gold deposits in the Lachlan Fold Belt of New South Wales, Australia. It holds an option to acquire a 100% interest in the Tottenham project comprising three granted exploration licenses covering an area of approximately 470 square kilometers located in the Cobar-Girilambone District in central New South Wales. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is based in Perth, Australia.
